### Frontend Override Rule (most important)

Three layers, three placement rules:

| Want to... | Put it in |
|------------|-----------|
| Change an existing CRM component/page | `frontend/src_override/<same relative path as upstream>` |
| Add a brand-new component/page/util | `frontend/src/...` |
| Edit the sidebar | `frontend/src/index.js` (`customSidebarItems`) |

Never edit `crm_build/` (wiped on every build) or `apps/crm/frontend/src/` (upstream).
Run `yarn check-conflicts` after CRM upstream updates.

