## App-Specific Rules

{% if app.name == "novizna_crm" -%}
- DocType naming: `crm_<noun>` prefix
- Override registry: every `src_override/` file mirrors an existing `apps/crm/frontend/src/` path one-for-one
- Sidebar additions: only via `frontend/src/index.js` `customSidebarItems`
- Vendor connectors: pure SDK code under `connectors/`; orchestration belongs in `api/`
{%- elif app.name == "novizna_pos" -%}
- TypeScript strict mode — no `any` without `// FIXME: typing` comment
- Pinia stores are the source of truth for shared state; composables wrap stores
- All API calls go through `src/boot/axios.ts` (centralized auth + interceptors)
- Offline queue: failed writes enqueue to Pinia store, retry on `online` event with exponential backoff
- Service Worker: new asset classes must be allowlisted in `quasar.config.ts` `pwa.workboxOptions`
{%- elif app.name == "invoice_ninja_integration" -%}
- DocType naming: `invoice_ninja_<noun>` prefix
- Custom fields on ERPNext doctypes: scoped via this app's fixture, not directly via property setter
- Sync logs to `Invoice Ninja Sync Logs` DocType
{%- elif app.name == "noviznaerp_payroll" -%}
- 73 DocTypes — largest custom app. Naming uses bare domain nouns (acceptable, but disambiguate with app prefix when adding new ones)
- **Known anti-patterns to watch when editing:** 11 occurrences of `frappe.db.sql(f"...")` flagged HIGH in [discovery AP-001](../../../../ai/erpnext-ai-forge/discovery/data/anti-pattern-findings.json). Do not add more.
{%- elif app.name == "cargo_management" -%}
- EasyPost + 17Track webhook receivers — every guest-allowed handler must verify signature first
- Parcel-related DocTypes live under `parcel_management/`
{%- elif app.name == "novizna_core" -%}
- Cross-app utility app. Currency exchange providers under `currency_exchange/`
- Requires `erpnext_location`
{%- elif app.name == "changemakers" -%}
- 52 DocTypes for nonprofit / member workflows
{%- elif app.name == "erpnext_location" -%}
- Location / geo extension for ERPNext
{%- endif %}

