## Common Commands

```bash
source env/bin/activate
bench --site novizna-v16 migrate          # after DocType/patch changes
bench --site novizna-v16 clear-cache      # after hooks changes
bench --site novizna-v16 export-fixtures --app {{ app.name }}   # capture Custom Fields / Workflows
{% if app.name == "novizna_crm" -%}
cd apps/novizna_crm/frontend && yarn dev  # frontend dev with hot reload
yarn check-conflicts                       # verify src_override/ pairs after CRM updates
{% elif app.name == "novizna_pos" -%}
cd apps/novizna_pos/novizna-pos-ui && quasar dev
{% endif -%}
```

